headline: Q2 Rundown: Lamb Weston (NYSE:LW) Vs Other Shelf-Stable Food Stocks
summary: The end of an earnings season can be a great time to discover new stocks and assess how companies are handling the current business environment. Let’s take a look at how Lamb Weston (NYSE:LW) and the rest of the shelf-stable food stocks fared in Q2.
